text: Evana Manandhar () (born 26 November 1991) in Kathmandu, Nepal is a Nepali Model, Business woman and the title winner of Miss Nepal 2015. She represened Nepal in Miss World 2015 which was held in Sanya, China. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models Category:People from Kathmandu Category:Miss Nepal winners
